<p class="md:mt-2 mb-2 md:w-1/3 md:pr-2">
  If you use pyribs in your research, please cite it as follows. Note that you
  will need to include the
  <a href="https://www.overleaf.com/learn/latex/Hyperlinks#Linking_web_addresses">hyperref</a>
  package in order to use the <code>\url</code> command.
</p>

<div class="w-full md:w-2/3 md:mb-4">
